Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sudden tragedy that hit the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Maico be able to continue the program without the script writer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Maico!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.65,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,fax: Aren't you airing Yukie-chan S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:06.00,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's a radio artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was, he wanted to stay on the scene until the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this program really worth that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it is or not is up to Suga himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has any right to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do for Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is to carry on with this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is to let Suga-san have the best program in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive even the smallest mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san, give me the best jingle ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Maico?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what. Just talk, Maico.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak for him, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't break. Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't goof up today, Maico!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radio drama, Yukie-chan S.O.S., will be off the air this week due to certain circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In its place, let me talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's me talk for the sake of my precious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, we had a serious problem in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The script writer, Suga-san, vomited blood and became unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the staff members ran up to him, and took him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just stood right where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't too shocked to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was measuring you with my built-in sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was recording the dropping surface temperature and the heart rate on my hard disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I run up to you, Suga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Suga-san's life was saved because of the data I provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My specs as an android came in useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if there is a person falling unconscious nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it better to run up to that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least other staff members did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to simulate which was the better action to take,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the logic fell into an eternal loop, and I couldn't come up with a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on asking Suga-san when he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since he was hospitalized, no visitors have been allowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't even see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my data, he has weakened significantly already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been only 5 months since I have been booted up, so I do not know much about Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Suga-san I know wears glasses, has a physique that has taken in too many calories,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and always liked to stick his thumb up for anything, and say "You're shining" and "You're glowing."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He liked to smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and liked to drink, but couldn't drink;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's Star-san's fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's a bit slow at writing scripts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the finished scripts usually contained 6% misspellings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also has a unique quirk that makes him write scripts faster when he sees other other people's misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this program got started, teamwork among the staff members didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quarrels never ceased,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and at times we got violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we have even boycotted the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only Suga-san was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remember his words...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That "I'm going to write as good and legendary of a script in this program as the one from 10 years ago,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"for Live from the North Pole Crossing."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That "I'm going to rise up and shine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Suga-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't enough information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk more about Suga-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is not enough data for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell him why I, an android, can be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came across well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's faltering, she wants to say more to Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we want to let her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's that reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think more about that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Vampire Unit-kun is always alone, and feeling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember reading such a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it shining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico-chan, Vampire Unit-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Unit-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try hard and remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try hard and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying, Maico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other then cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a letter sent to Maico's 30,000 Friends corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sent by the pen-name Vampire Unit-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The handwriting was that of Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I advised Suga-san through the microphone with my own words, as I thought on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept making mistakes too, and got yelled at by the director every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make mistakes all the time, but I believe I can put forward an effort not to make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ends if you give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san, please keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get healthy, and write the script for the program again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like not having any more new data about Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radio drama isn't over yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want you to create a new corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san, don't get defeated by the illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying, trying, and trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a nice poem written by this program's mixer, Ume-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to dedicate it with my own arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving me, Densuke-san, Director-san, and all the staff in the studio behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any scripts written by Suga-san in today's program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hear the next episode of the radio drama either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Suga-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,neither Izumi-san, Ume-san, or Kacchin-san need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that the stars are just burning matter, like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still let me wish upon you, dear stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see Suga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's voice is reaching Suga, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the best personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a sponsor or the agent. I won't hear any complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shining so brightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Kachi-ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Suga-san just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the hospital, Suga-san just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san, please try, try, and try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm praying for your safe being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:07.00,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Suga-chan, leaving you with a glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it was bothering me when I entered Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:24.98,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Today sorry there's nothing really nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimane and Tottori, which was which?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both look alike, and they're both near each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimane was known as Izumo a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but knowing that doesn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha! Haha! Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm going to go flirt with the cute angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Android Ana Maico 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:30.53,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Maico
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Maico
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico, I'm cheering for you from Heaven!
